  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is served between 7am and 10.30am on the terrace overlooking the sea. Enjoy fresh, homemade jams and yogurts, sweet options like cakes and connoli and hot choices too like omelettes and crepes. If you upgrade to half board you'll have dinner in the Archipelago Restaurant each evening. </p>
<p><strong>Il Cappero Restaurant</strong> boasts a Michelin Star and a stunning seaside terrace from where you can enjoy delicious food created by Executive Chef Giuseppe Biuso. The menu offers an innovative take on fresh, Sicilian ingredients and changes seasonally. Reservations are required.</p>
<p><strong>L’Archipelago Restaurant</strong> offers lunch and dinner on a lovely terrace overlooking the sea. Sicilian dishes are accompanied by a large choice of local and international drinks.</p>
<p><strong>I Grusoni Restaurant</strong> is the perfect spot for a casual, poolside lunch or laid back dinner (high season only). Enjoy fresh seafood, salads, pizza and sandwiches in a lovely setting surrounded by exotic plants and wild flowers.</p>
<p><strong>I Russuri Bar</strong> is an outdoor bar located close to the infinity pool and offers a wide choice of drinks and aperitifs. It's the best place on the island to watch the sun go down over the ocean with a cocktail.</p>
<p><strong>I Fraglioni Bar </strong>is the hotel's exclusive lounge bar. Sink into one of the comfy sofas on the terrace with a glass of wine or cocktail and enjoy stunning views of the whole resort.  </p>]]></cateringDescription>
