  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are elegantly decorated in a fresh Mediterranean style. They're about 23-27m², sleep two people and have a terrace that overlooks the gardens. Facilities include a air-conditioning, TV, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, safe, minibar, bath or shower and a hairdryer. </p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms </strong>are about 23-27m² and sleep two people. They have beautiful sea views and a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Premiere Rooms </strong>are about 35-40m² and sleep up to three people. The extra bed is a single sofa bed. These rooms have a terrace with lateral sea views. </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>are about 26-33m² and sleep two people. They have beautiful sea views from a furnished terrace. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are about 35m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a sofa bed). They have a balcony and sea views and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Suite Lipari </strong>is about 48m² and sleeps up to four people. It has a living room and a terrace with sea views. It's available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Master Suites </strong>are about 23-33m² and sleep two people. They have a lounge area and a private terrace with a whirlpool and sea views. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Superior &amp; Comfort Rooms for Sole Use </strong>are about 20m² and are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
